x4freetext: LNR Phasotron U-400M Cyclotron was
used.
The irradiation time was 27 min and the proton beam
intensity was about 3*10**14 protons per min.
Errors include contributions from those
associated with the statistical significance of
experimental results, those in measuring the target
thickness, and those in determining the detector
efficiency.
